'''2020年貝魯特爆炸事故'''（{{lang-ar|انفجار مرفأ بيروت 2020}}）是發生在2020年8月4日下午6時（格林威治标准時間2020年8月4日15:00）左右在[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]首都[[贝鲁特|贝鲁特]][[貝魯特港|貝魯特港]]發生的两起大型爆炸事故，造成重大人员伤亡和财产损失<ref>{{Cite web|title=Puissantes explosions à Beyrouth, au moins 73 morts et 3.700 blessés|url=https://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/forte-explosion-entendue-a-beyrouth-20200804|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2020-08-04|last=AFP|first=Le Figaro avec|work=Le Figaro.fr|language=fr|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124233433/https://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/forte-explosion-entendue-a-beyrouth-20200804|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Massive explosion shakes Lebanese capital, buildings near Beirut port reportedly damaged|url=https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/massive-explosion-shakes-lebanese-capital-buildings-near-beirut-port-damaged-1.9046138|accessdate=2020-08-04|date=2020-08-04|last1=Khoury|first1=Jack|last2=Landou|first2=Noa|website=Haaretz|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805065959/https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/massive-explosion-shakes-lebanese-capital-buildings-near-beirut-port-damaged-1.9046138|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Massive explosion shakes Lebanon's capital Beirut|url=https://www.sfchronicle.com/news/article/Massive-explosion-shakes-Lebanon-s-capital-Beirut-15457414.php|access-date=2020-08-04|website=San Francisco Chronicle|last1=Mroue|first1=Bassem|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806131303/https://www.sfchronicle.com/news/article/Massive-explosion-shakes-Lebanon-s-capital-Beirut-15457414.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last=Hubbard|first=Ben|date=2020-08-04|title=Explosions Rock East Beirut|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/04/world/middleeast/beirut-explosion-blast.html|access-date=2020-08-04|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804193448/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/04/world/middleeast/beirut-explosion-blast.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这场事故导致至少218人死亡，超過6,500人受傷且为数众多的人失踪<ref>{{Cite web|title=LIVE: France's Macron says Lebanon aid won't go to the 'corrupt'|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/lebanon-orders-house-arrest-officials-beirut-blast-live-200805230752876.html|accessdate=2020-08-06|author1=Ted Regencia|author2=Arwa Ibrahim|author3=Ramy Allahoum|work=Al Jazeera|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921042358/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/lebanon-orders-house-arrest-officials-beirut-blast-live-200805230752876.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|title=Beirut explosion: dead and wounded among 'hundreds of casualties', says Lebanon Red Cross – live updates|first1=Oliver|last1=Holmes|first2=Peter|last2=Beaumont|first3=Michael|last3=Safi|first4=Martin|last4=Chulov|date=2020-08-04|website=The Guardian|accessdate=2020-08-04|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804201541/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="jazeera.live.2020.08.04">{{Cite web|last=Gadzo|first=Mersiha|title=Dozens killed, thousands wounded in Beirut blast: Live updates|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|access-date=2020-08-04|date=2020-08-04|website=Al Jazeera|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804210957/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且導致30萬人無家可歸（距爆炸原點半徑3公里內共77萬居民）<ref>[https://edition.cnn.com/middleeast/live-news/lebanon-beirut-explosion-live-updates-dle-intl/index.html Beirut explosion rocks Lebanon's capital city] {{Wayback|url=https://edition.cnn.com/middleeast/live-news/lebanon-beirut-explosion-live-updates-dle-intl/index.html |date=20200805062133 }}CNN，2020年8月6日</ref><ref name=ds/>。黎巴嫩公共保安部称爆炸與2014年開始存放於港內的2,700噸[[硝酸铵|硝酸铵]]有關<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|title=Explosion 'caused by highly explosive material stored in warehouse': Official|website=Al Jazeera|date=2020-08-04|accessdate=2020-08-04|last1=Gadzo|first1=Mersiha|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804210957/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事故[[爆炸当量|爆炸当量]]大約在300至1000噸的[[三硝基甲苯|TNT]]之間<ref name="Horton 2020">{{cite web | last=Horton | first=Alex | title=Here’s what the videos of the Beirut blast tell us about the explosion | website=Washington Post | date=2020-08-04 | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2020/08/04/beirut-explosion-ammonium-nitrate/ | access-date=2020-08-05 | archive-date=2020-08-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819072657/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2020/08/04/beirut-explosion-ammonium-nitrate/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
黎巴嫩经济常年{{le|黎巴嫩流动性危机|Lebanese liquidity crisis|处于危机状态}}，政府一直拖欠债务，[[黎巴嫩镑|黎巴嫩镑]]暴跌，贫困率升至50%以上<ref name=balkiz />。

[[贝鲁特港|贝鲁特港]]是黎巴嫩的海上交通要道、稀缺商品进口的重要基础设施<ref name=azhari /><ref name=grzeszczak>{{cite web |last1=Grzeszczak |first1=Jocelyn |title=What is the Port of Beirut? Everything We Know About the Site Following Deadly Explosion |url=https://www.newsweek.com/what-port-beirut-everything-we-know-about-site-following-deadly-explosion-1522830 |website=Newsweek |accessdate=2020-08-05 |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805210708/https://www.newsweek.com/what-port-beirut-everything-we-know-about-site-following-deadly-explosion-1522830 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。港口由黎巴嫩政府持有，有4座港池、16处码头和12间仓库<ref name=grzeszczak />。还有一个可储备黎巴嫩85%战略用小麦的仓库，经济部长{{tsl|en|Raoul Nehme|拉乌尔·纳姆}}称该仓库被炸毁时仅存有1.5万吨小麦，这比当地官员所聲称，库存达12万吨的容量少很多<ref name=azhari /><ref>[https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2020/08/05/356108 【贝鲁特大爆炸】粮仓被炸毁　黎急寻储备地区] {{Wayback|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2020/08/05/356108 |date=20200824042959 }}东方日报，2020年8月5日</ref>。[[贝鲁特海军基地|贝鲁特海军基地]]也位于港口<ref name=grzeszczak />。

