2013年9月27日，悬挂[[摩尔多瓦|摩尔多瓦]]{{le|船只注册|ship registration|国旗}}船籍[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]的货运[[摩托船|摩托船]]{{tsl|en|MV Rhosus|
罗瑟斯号|“罗瑟斯号”}}搭载一家葡萄牙公司所購買的2,750吨[[硝酸铵|硝酸铵]]，从黑海沿岸的[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]][[巴统|巴统]]出发，前往東非國家[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]]的目的地[[贝拉|贝拉]]送貨<ref name="rhosus.shiparrested">{{cite journal |url=https://shiparrested.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/The-Arrest-News-11th-issue.pdf#page=3 |title=m/v Rhosus — Arrest and Personal Freedom of the Crew |date=October 2015 |number=11 |journal=The Arrest News |accessdate=2020-08-05 |first1=Charbel |last1=Dagher |first2=Christine |last2=Maksoud |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805004609/https://shiparrested.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/The-Arrest-News-11th-issue.pdf#page=3 |archive-date=2020-08-05 }}</ref><ref>[https://www.plataformamedia.com/zh-hant/2020/08/09/%E8%B2%9D%E9%AD%AF%E7%89%B9%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E7%A1%9D%E9%85%B8%E9%8A%A8%E7%94%B1%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%A8%82%E8%B3%BC/ 貝魯特爆炸：硝酸銨由葡萄牙公司訂購] {{Wayback|url=https://www.plataformamedia.com/zh-hant/2020/08/09/%E8%B2%9D%E9%AD%AF%E7%89%B9%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%EF%BC%9A%E7%A1%9D%E9%85%B8%E9%8A%A8%E7%94%B1%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%A8%82%E8%B3%BC/ |date=20200824042958 }}Plataforma，2020年8月9日</ref>。向東南往非洲的航行过程中，“罗瑟斯号”突遇引擎故障，被迫停靠贝鲁特港<ref name="rhosus.tv2">{{Cite news|last=Jørgensen|first=Lars Bach|date=2020-08-05|title=Ekspert forklarer, hvad der sandsynligvis skete i Beirut|language=da|trans-title=Expert explains what probably happened in Beirut|work=TV 2|url=https://nyheder.tv2.dk/udland/2020-08-05-ekspert-forklarer-hvad-der-sandsynligvis-skete-i-beirut|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-08-05|quote=The large amount of potentially dangerous fertilizer has been there since 2014, when the Moldavian ship Rhosus had to port due to engine problems.|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805232643/https://nyheder.tv2.dk/udland/2020-08-05-ekspert-forklarer-hvad-der-sandsynligvis-skete-i-beirut}}</ref>。经[[港口国监督|港口国监督]]检查后，认为“罗瑟斯号”不适合航行。“罗瑟斯号”原船長普羅科謝夫（Boris Prokoshev）憶述，船东還试图在当地加载几台重型机械以赚取额外的费用。<ref name=mp/>但船组人员认为货物太过沉重，拒绝承接<ref>{{Cite web|title=Captain astonished to find out his ship delivered Beirut explosive|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/captain-astonished-to-find-out-his-ship-delivered-beirut-explosive/|accessdate=2020-08-07|last=Litvinova|first=Daria|work=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022190049/https://www.timesofisrael.com/captain-astonished-to-find-out-his-ship-delivered-beirut-explosive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于没有錢支付港口费，“罗瑟斯号”被禁止离港<ref name="rhosus.fleetmon" /><ref name="rhosus.tv2" />。船上有8名乌克兰人和1名俄国人，后来在乌克兰领事的协助下，先行將5名乌克兰人遣返回国，滯留下的4人則看管船只<ref name="rhosus.newsmaker" />{{efn|消息人士指船上剩下4名船员，但另有人士指船长也留下来<ref name="rhosus.newsmaker"/><ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/>。}}。

但后来船东破产，承租人对船运不再感兴趣，船东于是将货船废弃<ref name="rhosus.newsmaker">{{cite news|url=https://newsmaker.md/ro/presa-substanta-care-a-provocat-explozia-din-beirut-a-fost-adusa-de-nava-unui-rus-sub-pavilionul-r-moldova|title=Substanța care a provocat explozia din Beirut a fost adusă de nava unui rus sub pavilionul R. Moldova|first=Stela|last=Untila|newspaper=NewsMaker|date=2020-08-05|accessdate=2020-08-05|language=ro|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805205705/https://newsmaker.md/ro/presa-substanta-care-a-provocat-explozia-din-beirut-a-fost-adusa-de-nava-unui-rus-sub-pavilionul-r-moldova|dead-url=no}}</ref>。船上的粮食迅速耗尽，船员们却因移民限制仍无法下船<ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/>。债权人另外还获得了三份针对货船的扣留手令{{efn|法庭可颁布命令“扣留”舰船，支持债权人针对船舶提出的{{le|海上留置权|maritime lien}}索赔<ref>{{cite news|date=2020-04-03|title=Points to Consider if your Ship is Arrested|first=Eugene|last=Cheng|work=West of England|url=https://www.westpandi.com/publications/news/points-to-consider-if-your-ship-is-arrested/#:~:text=An%20arrest%20is%20a%20court,of%20arrest%20and%20an%20affidavit.|accessdate=2020-08-05|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805205726/https://www.westpandi.com/publications/news/points-to-consider-if-your-ship-is-arrested/#:~:text=An%20arrest%20is%20a%20court,of%20arrest%20and%20an%20affidavit.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。}}<ref name="rhosus.newsmaker"/><ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/>。律师出于同情，认为仍留在船上的货物會對他們构成危险，就遣返這幾名歐洲籍船员要求提出申訴。船員被困船上11个月后，贝鲁特的紧急事务法官允许他們返回家园<ref name="rhosus.newsmaker"/><ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/><ref name=mp>[https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200808/s00014/1596825769266/%E8%B2%9D%E9%AD%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A316%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%89%A3%E6%9F%A5 貝魯特港口16職員遭扣查] {{Wayback|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200808/s00014/1596825769266/%E8%B2%9D%E9%AD%AF%E7%89%B9%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A316%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E6%89%A3%E6%9F%A5 |date=20200824043030 }}明报，2020年8月8日</ref>。危险货物于2014年带上岸，接下来的6年间一直放在港口的12号机库中，没有采取安全措施<ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/><ref name="rhosus.jazeera">{{cite news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/officials-knew-danger-beirut-port-years-200805032416684.html|title=Beirut blast: Tracing the explosives that tore the capital apart|first=Timour|last=Azhari|journal=Al Jazeera|date=2020-08-05|accessdate=2020-08-05|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805205657/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/officials-knew-danger-beirut-port-years-200805032416684.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rhosus.fleetmon">{{cite web |last1=Voytenko |first1=Mikhail |title=Crew kept hostages on a floating bomb — m/v Rhosus, Beirut |url=https://www.fleetmon.com/maritime-news/2014/4194/crew-kept-hostages-floating-bomb-mv-rhosus-beirut/ |website=fleetmon |date=2014-07-23 |access-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804213142/https://www.fleetmon.com/maritime-news/2014/4194/crew-kept-hostages-floating-bomb-mv-rhosus-beirut/ |archive-date=2020-08-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Rhosus |url=https://www.fleetmon.com/vessels/rhosus_8630344_46589/ |website=Fleetmon [vessel tracker database] |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807010659/https://www.fleetmon.com/vessels/rhosus_8630344_46589/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rhosus.shiparrested"/><ref name="Reuters Toll Expected">{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-security-blast/toll-expected-to-rise-in-blast-that-shook-beirut-killing-78-and-injuring-thousands-idUSKCN25107B|access-date=2020-08-05|date=2020-08-05|work=Reuters|title=Toll expected to rise in blast that shook Beirut, killing 78 and injuring thousands|last1=Nakhoul|first1=Samia|last2=Francis|first2=Ellen|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805092034/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-security-blast/toll-expected-to-rise-in-blast-that-shook-beirut-killing-78-and-injuring-thousands-idUSKCN25107B|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

爆炸發生後網上流傳相信是12號倉庫此前的照片，顯示裝有硝酸銨的袋上印有「NITROPILL HD」標誌。新聞調查網站{{tsl|en|Bellingcat|Bellingcat}}指出，澳洲企業Orica生產的一款礦山爆破用硝酸銨炸藥，便命名為「NITROPIL」，比「NITROPILL HD」少一個L，後者相信是由一家巴西公司生產的冒牌貨。<ref>[http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/08/06/GJ2008060009.htm 充公自扣押貨船 硝酸銨或巴西山寨貨] {{Wayback|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/08/06/GJ2008060009.htm |date=20200814124522 }}文汇报，2020年8月6日</ref>

多位海关官員致信法官，要求解决扣押货物並提出三個建議，即将貨物出口，交付予[[黎巴嫩陆军|黎巴嫩陆军]]，或是卖给私营的黎巴嫩炸药公司（{{lang|en|Lebanese Explosives Company}}）<ref name="rhosus.jazeera"/>。此后官员多次写信，其中2016年的信称法官没有回复之前的请求，考虑到“这些储存在机库的货物在不适当的气候条件下非常危险”，“乞求”尽快解决<ref name="rhosus.jazeera"/>。其中一名曾在2013年提出风险警告的黎巴嫩海关药物管制处处长优素福·斯卡夫（Joseph Skaf）上校于2017年神秘死亡，他的两份尸检报告相互矛盾，死因尚未正式确定。<ref>[https://tech.sina.com.cn/roll/2020-08-07/doc-iivhuipn7331766.shtml 阿媒：2017年神秘死亡的黎海关官员，曾要求将2750吨硝酸铵运出贝鲁特] {{Wayback|url=https://tech.sina.com.cn/roll/2020-08-07/doc-iivhuipn7331766.shtml |date=20200810051912 }}新浪，2020年8月7日</ref>

== 爆炸 ==
[[File:دخان_انفجار_بيروت_انتشر_في_كل_سماء_لبنان.webm|thumb]]
第一次爆炸的規模較小，僅在廠區範圍內，爆炸時可見類似烟火的閃光，現場升起了灰色的烟雾，随后是许多被描述为类似烟花的小型爆炸<ref name=":1" />。

第二次更猛烈的爆炸发生在[[UTC+03:00|當地時間]]18:08左右，爆炸波及貝魯特城市中心，空气中弥漫着红色的尘埃烟雾和[[蘑菇云|蘑菇云]]<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Massive explosion rocks central Beirut|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/beirut-explosion-lebanon-harbour-port-a9653696.html|access-date=2020-08-04|website=The Independent|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804214723/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/beirut-explosion-lebanon-harbour-port-a9653696.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此次爆炸於[[以色列|以色列]]北部及[[賽普勒斯|賽普勒斯]]皆有震感，離事發地點遠達{{Cvt|240|km|mi|0|abbr=off}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-middle-east-53656328|title=Beirut explosion updates: Massive blast rocks Lebanese capital|website=BBC News|accessdate=2020-08-05|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804175009/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-middle-east-53656328|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=‘Like an earthquake’: Huge explosion rips through Beirut captured on video|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/two-explosions-rocks-lebanon-s-beirut-dozens-wounded-videos-surface-online/story-wkCeUkZGBqxMPVtrneAnNI.html|access-date=2020-08-04|website=Hindustan Times|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805062135/https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/two-explosions-rocks-lebanon-s-beirut-dozens-wounded-videos-surface-online/story-wkCeUkZGBqxMPVtrneAnNI.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於第一次爆炸後許多民眾已經以手機拍攝，遂紀錄到第二次大爆炸，衝擊波形成了圓拱型的凝結雲<ref name=":1" />，而爆炸畫面也迅速透過社群網站散佈至全球。据目击者说，{{Cvt|10|km|mi|0|abbr=off}}外的房屋被炸毁<ref name="balkiz" />。而据[[贝鲁特省|贝鲁特省长]]{{link-en|马尔万·阿布德|Marwan Abboud}}说，在此之前发生了一场火灾<ref name="guardian-lebanon-at-least-73-killed">{{Cite news|title=Beirut explosion: at least 100 dead and 4,000 wounded – live updates|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|last=Chulov|first=Martin|date=2020-08-04|access-date=2020-08-04|work=The Guardian|last2=Safi|first2=Michael|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804201541/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]和[[欧洲与地中海地震中心|欧洲与地中海地震中心]]均测定，这次爆炸相当于[[近震震级|M<sub>L</sub>]] 3.3的地震<ref name="usgs">{{Cite web |url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us6000b9bx/executive |title=M 3.3 Explosion - 1 km ENE of Beirut, Lebanon |publisher=[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]] |access-date=2020-08-05 |date=2020-08-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808140548/https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/us6000b9bx/executive |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=882410 |title=M 3.3 - LEBANON - SYRIA REGION - 2020-08-04 15:08:18 UTC |publisher=[[欧洲与地中海地震中心|欧洲与地中海地震中心]] |access-date=2020-08-05 |date=2020-08-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824043139/https://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=882410 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但美国地质调查局强调，其测定的震级不能直接与类似规模的天然地震直接做比较，因为爆炸发生在地震波生成效率不高的地表处<ref name=usgs />。[[谢菲尔德大学|谢菲尔德大学]]的专家估计此次爆炸是历史上影响最大的非核爆炸<ref>{{cite news |title=Port officials under house arrest after Beirut blast |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-53670839 |publisher=BBC News |location= |date=2020-08-06 |access-date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117051336/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-53670839 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，事故起因类似于2015年[[2015年天津港危化品倉庫爆炸事故|中国天津]]和1947年[[德克萨斯城灾难|德克萨斯城]]的硝酸铵爆炸事故<ref>{{cite news |title=What we know about the massive chemical explosion in Beirut |url=https://arstechnica.com/science/2020/08/what-we-know-about-the-massive-chemical-explosion-in-beirut/ |work=Ars Technica |date=2020-08-05 |accessdate=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806060643/https://arstechnica.com/science/2020/08/what-we-know-about-the-massive-chemical-explosion-in-beirut/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Expert reaction to Beirut explosion |url=https://www.sciencemediacentre.org/expert-reaction-to-beirut-explosion/ |work= |date=2020-08-05 |accessdate=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073610/https://www.sciencemediacentre.org/expert-reaction-to-beirut-explosion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要的大火于第二天扑灭<ref>{{cite web |last1=Brumfiel |first1=Geoff |title=Satellite Images Show Aftermath Of Beirut Blast |url=https://www.npr.org/2020/08/05/899299228/satellite-images-show-aftermath-of-beirut-blast |website=NPR |accessdate=2020-08-09 |date=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115104834/https://www.npr.org/2020/08/05/899299228/satellite-images-show-aftermath-of-beirut-blast |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

俄羅斯军事专家維克·穆拉霍夫斯基（Viktor Murakhovsky）在接受《[[共青团真理报|共青团真理报]]》采访时称，大部分硝酸铵可能已经被偷走，如果爆炸的硝酸铵数量真的达到了2,750吨，那么整个贝鲁特“会从地图上消失”。<ref>[https://www.enanyang.my/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/%E4%BF%84%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%A1%9D%E9%85%B8%E9%93%B5%E6%88%96%E5%A4%B1%E7%AA%83-%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%A8%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E6%81%90%E6%8A%B9%E5%B9%B3%E8%B4%9D%E9%B2%81%E7%89%B9 俄专家:港口大量硝酸铵或失窃 若全爆炸恐抹平贝鲁特] {{Wayback|url=https://www.enanyang.my/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/%E4%BF%84%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%A1%9D%E9%85%B8%E9%93%B5%E6%88%96%E5%A4%B1%E7%AA%83-%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%A8%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E6%81%90%E6%8A%B9%E5%B9%B3%E8%B4%9D%E9%B2%81%E7%89%B9 |date=20200824043217 }}e南洋，2020年8月10日</ref><ref>[https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2020/08/09/Beirut-would-be-erased-had-full-chemical-load-exploded-bulk-likely-stolen-Expert Beirut would be ‘erased’ had full chemical load exploded, bulk likely stolen: Expert] {{Wayback|url=https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2020/08/09/Beirut-would-be-erased-had-full-chemical-load-exploded-bulk-likely-stolen-Expert |date=20201010064005 }}Al Arabiya Network，2020年8月9日</ref>

===起因===
爆炸的起因未能即時判斷<ref name="azhari">{{cite web |last1=Azhari |first1=Timour |title=Hundreds wounded as huge blast rips through Lebanon's Beirut |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/large-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-200804153400078.html |website=Al Jazeera |accessdate=2020-08-04 |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804163013/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/large-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-200804153400078.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，黎巴嫩媒体起初报道指烟火儲存仓发生爆炸；有部分其他报道則稱該處為石油或化學品儲存设施<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Multiple explosions rock Downtown Beirut: Eyewitnesses|url=https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2020/08/04/Smoke-seen-from-possible-explosion-near-port-area-in-Lebanon-s-Beirut.html|access-date=2020-08-04|publisher=Al Arabiya English|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804153400/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2020/08/04/Smoke-seen-from-possible-explosion-near-port-area-in-Lebanon-s-Beirut.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Huge explosion in Beirut shatters windows and rocks buildings|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/04/huge-explosion-beirut-lebanon-shatters-windows-rocks-buildings|access-date=2020-08-04|website=The Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804160549/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/04/huge-explosion-beirut-lebanon-shatters-windows-rocks-buildings|dead-url=no}}</ref>。港口內有倉庫儲存化學品與爆炸品，當中包括[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]（一種常見的肥料及炸藥原料）<ref name="reuters">{{cite web |title=Massive blast in Beirut kills at least 10, sending shockwaves across city |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-security-blast/massive-blast-in-beirut-kills-at-10-dead-sending-shockwaves-across-city-idUSKCN25021M |website=[[路透社|Reuters]] |accessdate=2020-08-04 |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819072650/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lebanon-security-blast/massive-blast-in-beirut-kills-at-10-dead-sending-shockwaves-across-city-idUSKCN25021M |dead-url=no }}</ref>。黎巴嫩公共保安部長指爆炸由沒收的[[硝酸铵|硝酸铵]]引起<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|title=Explosion 'caused by highly explosive material stored in warehouse': Official|publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2020-08-04|access-date=2020-08-04|author=Gadzo, Mersiha|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804210957/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/huge-explosion-rocks-lebanon-capital-beirut-live-updates-200804163620414.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

美国总统[[唐納·特朗普|唐納·特朗普]]宣称爆炸不是因为某种意外，而是炸弹袭击，但隨後[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]稱「截至目前尚未取得任何線索顯示，這是一起『攻擊事件』」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=偷藏6年的城市爆彈！貝魯特大爆炸...已知78死4,000傷|url=https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4756621|accessdate=2020-08-05|last=聯合新聞網|work=轉角國際 udn Global|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128174548/https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4756621|dead-url=no}}</ref>

{{le|黎巴嫩国际广播公司|Lebanese Broadcasting Corporation International}}报道指，出席国防委员会高级简报会的人士说，大火是由在仓库焊接门的工人点燃的<ref name="cause.national">{{cite news|url=https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/what-caused-the-beirut-explosion-everything-we-know-so-far-1.1059236|title=What caused the Beirut explosion? Everything we know so far|first=Liz|last=Cookman|date=2020-08-05|work=The National|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073626/https://www.thenationalnews.com/world/mena/what-caused-the-beirut-explosion-everything-we-know-so-far-1.1059236|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cause.hindustan">{{cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/beirut-blast-warnings-of-extreme-danger-ignored-by-lebanon-officials-about-stored-ammonium-nitrate/story-Sd2AA6YZmJ9PwbPZhUd6SK.html|title=Beirut blast: Warnings of 'extreme danger' ignored by Lebanon officials about stored ammonium nitrate|date=2020-08-05|first=Arpan|last=Rai|work=Hindustan Times|accessdate=2020-08-09|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073617/https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/beirut-blast-warnings-of-extreme-danger-ignored-by-lebanon-officials-about-stored-ammonium-nitrate/story-Sd2AA6YZmJ9PwbPZhUd6SK.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{efn|最初报道引述一名安全部门消息人士，指大火是因仓库内修复一处破洞的焊接工作引起<ref name="Reuters Toll Expected" />。}}。一名前港口工人表示，12号仓库内有30至40个尼龙袋装满了烟花<ref name="GDNPortWorker">{{cite news |title=Beirut explosion: former port worker says fireworks stored in hangar |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/07/beirut-explosion-former-port-worker-says-fireworks-stored-in-hangar |accessdate=2020-08-07 |work=The Guardian |date=2020-08-07 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113111615/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/07/beirut-explosion-former-port-worker-says-fireworks-stored-in-hangar |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

56岁的“炸彈先生”达尼洛·科佩（Danilo Coppe）是意大利领先的爆破专家之一。他说，现场影片显示，爆炸时产生的蘑菇云是橙色的，如果只是储存在港口的2,750吨硝酸铵爆炸，蘑菇云颜色将会是黄色。他说：“应该有一个催化剂，否则不会全部一起爆炸。第二次爆炸时可以清楚地看到鲜红色的云，这是金属锂爆炸的典型特点，金属锂是军用导弹的推进剂，因此我认为仓库里還有军备物资。”<ref name=jf>[https://www.jfdaily.com/news/detail?id=278419 意大利爆破专家：贝鲁特爆炸起因不是硝酸铵，或是军用导弹] {{Wayback|url=https://www.jfdaily.com/news/detail?id=278419 |date=20200824043312 }}上觀，2020年8月11日</ref>

此前，[[美国中央情报局|美国中央情报局]]（CIA）的一名前特工贝尔也猜测，爆炸如此强烈，发生爆炸的可能不只是硝酸铵。此人曾在黎巴嫩工作多年，他在看过爆炸影片后推测称，第一次爆炸可能是硝酸铵导致的，但第二次爆炸明显是一次“军事爆炸”，“你看到那个橘黄色的火球了吗，这明显是军事爆炸，我很肯定那不是硝酸铵”。他还推测称发生爆炸的可能是一处军火库，但尚不明确其具体所属。<ref name=jf/>

== 傷亡 ==
