从现场拍摄的影片中可見有汽車和建築物的覆面被掀起<ref name="BBC-53656220">{{cite web |title=Many injured as large blast rocks Beirut |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-53656220 |publisher=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]] |accessdate=2020-08-04 |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804163034/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-53656220 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，目擊者称10公里外的住宅亦受到破壞，爆炸使多達30萬人流離失所<ref name="balkiz">{{cite news |last1=Qiblawi |first1=Tamara |title=Beirut explosion shatters windows across Lebanese capital |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/04/middleeast/beirut-explosion-port-intl/index.html |accessdate=2020-08-04 |publisher=CNN |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804212749/https://www.cnn.com/2020/08/04/middleeast/beirut-explosion-port-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直升机向起火建筑播散水弹<ref name="jazeera.live.2020.08.04"/>。黎巴嫩政府称城市內第二大[[穀倉塔|穀倉塔]]遭摧毀<ref>{{Cite web|title=These offices were 1.5km from the blast, and had a grain elevator as a buffer in between, and it still did this. Beirut off of the The Daily Star in the Merkaziah Plaza Bayrut, Beirut Governorate - Lebanon news on live map - lebanon.liveuamap.com|url=https://lebanon.liveuamap.com/en/2020/4-august-these-offices-were-15km-from-the-blast-and-had-a|access-date=2020-08-04|website=Lebanon news on live map  - lebanon.liveuamap.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026222612/https://lebanon.liveuamap.com/en/2020/4-august-these-offices-were-15km-from-the-blast-and-had-a|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Sullivan (now)|first=Helen|last2=Holmes (earlier)|first2=Oliver|last3=Safi|first3=Michael|date=2020-08-04|title=Beirut explosion: more than 50 dead and 2,750 wounded, says Lebanon health ministry – live updates|language=en-GB|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|access-date=2020-08-04|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804201541/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2020/aug/04/beirut-explosion-huge-blast-port-lebanon-capital|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使因[[2019冠狀病毒病黎巴嫩疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]而發生的糧食短缺更為惡化<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200701-food-insecurity-hits-middle-class-amid-lebanon-s-economic-crisis |title=Food insecurity hits middle class amid Lebanon's economic crisis |last=Molana-Allen |first=Leila |date=2020-07-01 |website=France 24 |access-date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2020-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702094255/https://www.france24.com/en/20200701-food-insecurity-hits-middle-class-amid-lebanon-s-economic-crisis |dead-url=no }}</ref>。黎巴嫩政府已部署直升机以撲滅爆炸引發的火災<ref name="jazeera.live.2020.08.04"/>。

贝鲁特的三所医院完全被毁，另有两所受损<ref name="AJE 05-08">{{cite news|work=[[半島電視台英語頻道|Al Jazeera English]] |title=Lebanon eyes state of emergency after deadly Beirut blast: Live|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/lebanon-eyes-state-emergency-deadly-beirut-blast-live-200804234925493.htm|date=2020-08-05|access-date=2020-08-05}}</ref>。由于医院被毁，数十名被送往临近医院的伤者无法入院。离事发现场不到{{Cvt|1|km|mi}}的{{tsl|en|Saint George Hospital University Medical Center|圣乔治医科大学医疗中心}}的病人由于医院被毁，在大街上接受治疗<ref name=":2" />，首都的醫療資源和人力嚴重不足。

[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]][[报纸|报纸]]《{{tsl|en|The Daily Star (Lebanon)|每日星报 (黎巴嫩)|每日星报}}》的总部遭到严重破坏，部分屋顶被掀翻，窗户被吹起，家具被损坏。几十公里外都能听到和感觉到爆炸声——爆炸的冲击波一直延伸到{{Cvt|200|km|mi|0|abbr=off}}多外的[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.fr/entry/explosions-beyrouth-liban-ce-que-lon-sait_fr_5f29a59ec5b6a34284c03c62|title=Beyrouth: Ce que l'on sait des explosions au Liban|author=|date=2020-08-04|work=Le HuffPost|publisher=|accessdate=2020-08-04|language=fr|format=|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210153244/https://www.huffingtonpost.fr/entry/explosions-beyrouth-liban-ce-que-lon-sait_fr_5f29a59ec5b6a34284c03c62|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

首都贝鲁特共有{{tsl|en|List of diplomatic missions in Lebanon|驻黎巴嫩外交机构列表|72国大使馆}}。贝鲁特城内外多座大使馆建筑遭受不同程度的损毁。靠近爆炸地点的澳大利亚和芬兰大使馆严重受损<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=Australian embassy 'considerably' damaged in Beirut blast, one Australian killed|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-08-05/australian-embassy-damaged-in-beirut-blast/12525330|access-date=2020-08-05|website=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805091656/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-08-05/australian-embassy-damaged-in-beirut-blast/12525330|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Report: Finnish Embassy in Beirut ‘destroyed’ by blast|url=https://newsnowfinland.fi/finland-international/report-finnish-embassy-in-beirut-destroyed-by-blast|access-date=2020-08-05|website=News Now Finland|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805091650/https://newsnowfinland.fi/finland-international/report-finnish-embassy-in-beirut-destroyed-by-blast|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而离现场{{convert|7.3|km|mi|0|abbr=off}}的韩国大使馆受损轻微，两扇窗户破损<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-05|title=No S. Koreans Reported Killed or Injured in Beirut Explosions|url=http://world.kbs.co.kr/service/news_view.htm?lang=e&Seq_Code=155355|access-date=2020-08-05|website=KBS World Radio|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805093406/http://world.kbs.co.kr/service/news_view.htm?lang=e&Seq_Code=155355|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，哈萨克<ref name="russokazakhembassies">{{Cite news |website=BBC News Русская служба |publisher=BBC News |title=Мощный взрыв в Бейруте: масштабные разрушения, десятки погибших и тысячи пострадавших |url=https://www.bbc.com/russian/news-53656494 |language=ru |accessdate=2020-08-04 |date=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073542/https://www.bbc.com/russian/news-53656494 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、俄罗斯<ref name="russokazakhembassies" />、罗马尼亚<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.romania-insider.com/beirut-explosion-ro-embassy-aug-2020 |title=Beirut explosion: Romanian embassy HQ slightly damaged |date=2020-08-05 |website=Romania Insider |accessdate=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073606/https://www.romania-insider.com/beirut-explosion-ro-embassy-aug-2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和土耳其<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/tr/dunya/beyrut-taki-patlamalarda-2-turk-vatandasi-yaralandi/1931621 |title=Beyrut'taki patlamalarda 2 Türk vatandaşı yaralandı |agency=Anadolu Agency |language=tr |date=2020-08-04 |accessdate=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204073546/https://www.aa.com.tr/tr/dunya/beyrut-taki-patlamalarda-2-turk-vatandasi-yaralandi/1931621 |dead-url=no }}</ref>大使馆轻微受损。

多位隶属于{{le|联合国驻黎巴嫩临时部队|United Nations Interim Force in Lebanon}}的[[联合国维持和平部队|海军维和队员]]受伤，另有一艘舰船受损<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-04|title=Lebanon: UN ‘actively assisting’ in response to huge explosions at Beirut port|url=https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/08/1069542|access-date=2020-08-05|website=UN News|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200805120513/https://news.un.org/en/story/2020/08/1069542|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

爆炸发生后港口出现一个直径约140公尺的大坑，對比港口原貌差異很大，附近的市集與寺院均受破壞，也毀掉了一些醫療物資<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-53697457 黎巴嫩贝鲁特大爆炸：图说历劫前后] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-53697457 |date=20201101071528 }}BBC中文，2020年8月8日</ref>，並導致停泊在港口的一艘[[遠洋定期船|郵輪]]「[[東方女王號|東方女王號]]」沉沒，該船在爆炸後受到嚴重損毀，並有2名船員死亡及7名船員受傷，郵輪公司嘗試拯救船隻但不果，最終沉沒。<ref>[http://news.hsw.cn/system/2020/0806/1220257.shtml 触目惊心！黎巴嫩首都大爆炸前后卫星图对比] {{Wayback|url=http://news.hsw.cn/system/2020/0806/1220257.shtml |date=20200925140109 }}華商網，2020年8月6日</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=【黎巴嫩爆炸・最新】至少100死4000傷 25萬人無家可歸|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/506963/黎巴嫩爆炸-最新-至少100死4000傷-25萬人無家可歸|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2020-08-05|last=成依華|first=梁凱怡, 王慧珊, 許懿安|work=香港01|language=zh-HK}}</ref>

距离爆炸现场约10公里的[[贝鲁特-拉菲克·哈里里国际机场|贝鲁特-拉菲克·哈里里国际机场]]受损轻微<ref>{{cite web |title=Beirut airport damaged in explosion, but flights continue |url=https://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/travel/beirut-airport-damaged-in-explosion-but-flights-continue-1.1059310 |website=The National |accessdate=2020-08-07 |date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930070140/https://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/travel/beirut-airport-damaged-in-explosion-but-flights-continue-1.1059310 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，门、窗户和天花板被冲击波震碎，电线被切断。尽管受到了破坏，但爆炸发生后航班仍陆续抵达<ref>{{cite web |last1=Perton |first1=Ted |title=Beirut Airport Continues Operation Despite Heavy Damage |url=https://samchui.com/2020/08/06/beirut-airport-continues-operation-despite-heavy-damage/ |website=SamChui.com |accessdate=2020-08-07 |date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017060831/https://samchui.com/2020/08/06/beirut-airport-continues-operation-despite-heavy-damage/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由日本逃亡到黎巴嫩，陷入醜聞的法籍前[[日產汽車|雷諾日產汽車]]行政總裁[[卡洛斯·戈恩|卡洛斯·戈恩]]位處貝魯特的住宅亦受到破壞，他的妻子表明沒有人在爆炸中受傷<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2020080500305&g=int |title=ベイルート大爆発でゴーン被告宅も被害　ブラジル紙 |accessdate=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208041351/https://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2020080500305&g=int |dead-url=no }}</ref>；日本网友表示可到日本免費吃住，暗諷其2019年12月30日未經審訊即[[棄保潛逃|棄保潛逃]]，戈恩此前稱日本政府將其禁足是對其迫害。<ref>[https://www.sohu.com/a/411572876_313745 戈恩住宅在贝鲁特爆炸中被毁，日本网友：来我们这吃住免费] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/411572876_313745 |date=20200824043754 }}搜狐，2020-08-05</ref>

